      "content": "I hear you and the profound exhaustion you're feeling. It's crucial to take things one step at a time, even when it feels overwhelming. Focus on one small, manageable goal each day, whether it's taking a few deep breaths, remembering a moment of joy, or engaging in a small activity you used to enjoy. These small actions can help bridge the distance you're feeling and bring some meaning back to your life. Professional help, like therapy, might also provide you with new tools and perspectives to navigate these feelings. Remember, you're more than what you're going through, and there are people and resources out there ready to support you.",
